003d\"Image\" alt\u003d\"The Maersk Gallant drilling rig\" title\u003d\"The Maersk Gallant drilling rig. (Photo: Ole Jørgen Bratland)\" srcset\u003d\"/content/dam/statoil/image/news/2016-february/gallant.jpg.transform/extra-small/image.jpg 100w, /content/dam/statoil/image/news/2016-february/gallant.jpg.transform/small/image.jpg 768w, /content/dam/statoil/image/news/2016-february/gallant.jpg.transform/medium/image.jpg 1024w, /content/dam/statoil/image/news/2016-february/gallant.jpg.transform/large/image.jpg 1537w,/content/dam/statoil/image/news/2016-february/gallant.jpg.transform/extra-large/image.jpg 2000w\"\u003e \n        \u003c/div\u003e \n        \u003cfigcaption class\u003d\"figure-module_reference small\"\u003e \n         \u003cdiv class\u003d\"figure-module_caption small\"\u003e\n           The Maersk Gallant drilling rig. (Photo: Ole Jørgen Bratland) \n         \u003c/div\u003e \n        \u003c/figcaption\u003e \n       \u003c/figure\u003e \n      \u003c/div\u003e \n     \u003c/div\u003e \n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"text parbase section\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"component-container base undefined \" data-emptytext\u003d\"Text\"\u003e \n       \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class\u003d\"ingress\"\u003eStatoil has decided to cancel the contract with Maersk Gallant.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \n      \u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003c/div\u003e \n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"text parbase section\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"component-container base undefined \" data-emptytext\u003d\"Text\"\u003e \n       \u003cp\u003eThe Maersk rig has been on contract with Statoil for two years, since 21 August 2014, and since 9 October it has been sub-chartered to ConocoPhillips.\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e Between 14 February and 21 August 2016 the Maersk Gallant is on a new contract with Total, who will pay cancellation fee according to the former contract.\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e Please contact Total for further information about the rig plans.\u003c/p\u